Maintenance commands
apt-get update. Run this command after changing /etc/apt/sources.list or /etc/apt/preferences . ...
apt-get upgrade. ...
apt-get check. ...
apt-get -f install. ...
apt-get autoclean. ...
apt-get clean. ...
dpkg-reconfigure <package_name> ...
echo "<package_name> hold" | dpkg --set-selections.
